fix: validate table names against allowlist to prevent SQL injection (he-fjn)

Add allowlist validation for dynamic table names in fmt.Sprintf SQL
queries in deleteByID, searchByEmbedding (entities/store.go) and
searchTable (tools/entities.go). While callers currently pass only
hardcoded table names, the unvalidated pattern is a latent injection
vector.

